\"entities\": [{\"begin\": 715, \"end\": 718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3631605885595204e-16, \"text\": \"MVP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.451821544299869e-31, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Lakers star has won two Olympic gold medals - in 2012 and in 2008 aspart of the so-called \\\"Redeem Team\\\"- though it is likely that those at home will judge him more on his achievements in the NBA than forTeam USA.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1115, \"end\": 1118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.451821544299869e-31, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1132, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9241298699938423, \"rank\": 0.08196633113657888, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"James will never beat the record for the highest number of NBA titles won, but he will arrive in Paris looking to extend a legacy that, for some, is already the most impressive in the sport.\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1138, \"end\": 1143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.028170374081485e-28, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 1197, \"end\": 1200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.451821544299869e-31, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999862625374, \"rank\": 1.3737575805887998e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 39-year-old has also been announced asTeam USA's flag bearer for the opening ceremony, along with tennis star Coco Gauff.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9241298699938423, \"rank\": 0.08196633113657888, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1443, \"end\": 1453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Coco Gauff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coco_Gauff\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he will make his return to the Olympic stage atParis 2024as part of a star-studded Team USA side that includes fellowNBA stars Steph Curry, Kevin Durant and Anthony Davis.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3538791372097967e-16, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1587, \"end\": 1598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steph Curry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephen_Curry\"}, {\"begin\": 1606, \"end\": 1612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.85689832181628e-29, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}, {\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2153481638822286e-40, \"text\": \"Anthony Davis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Davis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Born in Akron, Ohio in December 1984, James was introduced to basketball aged nine, and began playing organised games in the fifth grade.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1671, \"end\": 1676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.028170374081485e-28, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He later attended St. Vincent-St. Mary High School, a local private Catholic school, and by the end of his senior year, he had been named as the National Player of the Year twice in a row.\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1840, \"end\": 1855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_school\", \"score\": 0.9999997587156322, \"rank\": 2.412845362393435e-07, \"text\": \"Catholic school\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_school\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_school\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following his immensely successful high school career, James went straight into the 2003 NBA draft as first pick, becoming one of a small number of players to enter the draft without first playing college basketball - somethingknown as going 'prep-to-pro'.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2017, \"end\": 2022, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.028170374081485e-28, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 2046, \"end\": 2060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2003_NBA_draft\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2003 NBA draft\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2003_NBA_draft\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2003_NBA_draft\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was picked by the Cleveland Cavaliers and his success continued once professional, as he claimed the Rookie of the Year award and became only the third player in league history to average at least 20 points, five rebounds, and five assists per game in their debut season.\", \"from\": 2220, \"to\": 2494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2241, \"end\": 2260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.420495373837981e-60, \"text\": \"Cleveland Cavaliers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cleveland_Cavaliers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His Olympic career began in Sydney in 2004, though that edition ended in disappointment as Team USA could only secure a bronze medal in a performance met with widespread derision in the States.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2524, \"end\": 2530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Swans\", \"score\": 0.7616383355984753, \"rank\": 0.19351098701147468, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Swans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney_Swans\"}, {\"begin\": 2587, \"end\": 2595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3538791372097967e-16, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"2008 arrived with equal amounts of pressure and promise, as a Team USA squad travelled to Beijing as clear favourites.\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2753, \"end\": 2761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3538791372097967e-16, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2781, \"end\": 2788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999918145, \"rank\": 6.043902232054035e-12, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"James played his part in collecting gold alongside Kobe Bryant, Chris Paul and Carmelo Anthony.\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2905, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2810, \"end\": 2815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.028170374081485e-28, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 2861, \"end\": 2872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9942627711496997, \"rank\": 0.005770334580237972, \"text\": \"Kobe Bryant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}, {\"begin\": 2874, \"end\": 2884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Paul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2107132532573691e-35, \"text\": \"Chris Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Paul\"}, {\"begin\": 2889, \"end\": 2904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carmelo_Anthony\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carmelo Anthony\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carmelo_Anthony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carmelo_Anthony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By 2012, James was established among the best in the NBA, and had made a controversial decision to move to Miami Heat two years earlier.\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 3043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2916, \"end\": 2921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.028170374081485e-28, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 2960, \"end\": 2963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.451821544299869e-31, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His decision paid off, as he won his first NBA championship ahead of once again competing at theOlympics.\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3087, \"end\": 3103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\", \"score\": 0.999848809404205, \"rank\": 0.000151208873737177, \"text\": \"NBA championship\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Team USA travelled to London 2012 with an equally talented - if not more so - roster, with the 2008 names joined by Durant, Davis and Russell Westbrook, as theUS romped to the gold medal matchbefore a narrow victory against Spain gave LeBron his second gold medal.\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3151, \"end\": 3159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3538791372097967e-16, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3173, \"end\": 3184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999998055159456, \"rank\": 1.9448391046253642e-07, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3267, \"end\": 3273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.85689832181628e-29, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}, {\"begin\": 3285, \"end\": 3302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russell_Westbrook\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Russell Westbrook\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russell_Westbrook\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russell_Westbrook\"}, {\"begin\": 3375, \"end\": 3380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998122716464274, \"rank\": 0.0001877632206934066, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"James withdrewfrom the Olympic squads in 2016 and 2021, and though he's won another three NBA championships since 2012 - including one with his beloved Cavs in 2016 - his NBA fortunes have waned since last winning the championship, with the LA Lakers in 2020.\", \"from\": 3417, \"to\": 3676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3417, \"end\": 3422, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.028170374081485e-28, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 3507, \"end\": 3510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.451821544299869e-31, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 3588, \"end\": 3591, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.451821544299869e-31, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 3658, \"end\": 3667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Lakers\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.578538290124e-55, \"text\": \"LA Lakers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Lakers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles_Lakers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Lakers lost in the first round of the playoffs last season, but the Olympics offers yet another chance for glory for the sport's greatest still-active player.\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At age 39, this could well be LeBron's final chance at a gold medal and international success with Team USA.\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 3950, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3941, \"end\": 3949, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.3538791372097967e-16, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with a new contract with the Lakers allowing him to fulfil his dreamof playing alongside son Bronny- and with a home Olympics on the horizon - do not rule out seeing The King on court in LA in 2028.\", \"from\": 3951, \"to\": 4153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4155, \"to\": 4385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4206, \"end\": 4217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 0.999999832852623, \"rank\": 1.515692624454579e-07, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"